body.body: When fitting heated grips to handlebars, dealers are requested to check the handlebar for burrs and sharp edges around the access holes/slots in the handlebar which may damage the heated grip harness.
If burrs or sharp edges are found, carefully remove them using a suitable file or emery paper.
Areas to check for burrs or sharp edges
